  "heading_path": "中文学术纯文风 Humanize Skill：生产化交付与红队报告 / 20. 第十六轮：把“人工读过”与“人写来源”彻底拆开 / 20.2 被撤销的 14 张正向卡",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 32,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01190:1abb83ad4f9d]]\n三份来源现在保留 ID、路径、provenance 和排除理由，但 role 改为\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01191:f76e21f105b1]]。构建器不打开这些文件，复制检查也不把它们重新纳入：\n\n| 来源 | 撤销卡数 | 撤销动作 |\n|---|---:|---|\n| [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01192:34e90b047a61]] | 1 | [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01193:f42161173887]] |\n| [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01194:dcd5246d1532]] | 7 | data role、identifiability、handoff、controlled contrast、trajectory classification、process/outcome、explanation boundary |\n| [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01195:293576ca7b3d]] | 6 | intervention isolation、proxy fallback、endpoint/trajectory、budget comparison、negative control、backend boundary |\n\n被删除的完整 ID 为：\n\n1. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01196:f42161173887]]；\n2. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01197:0f5987b42049]]；\n3. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01198:096ef4ed0224]]；\n4. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01199:ca1038885d73]]；\n5. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01200:7eaf054229f8]]；\n6. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01201:5660ad401f4f]]；\n7. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01202:b8de49e17ec9]]；\n8. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01203:8a0b636b40af]]；\n9. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01204:2c4fdd1c6382]]；\n10. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01205:16b70872c3dc]]；\n11. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01206:717e1707bab8]]；\n12. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01207:09283e94f423]]；\n13. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01208:de692c74819e]]；\n14. [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01209:7b2c687c1984]]。\n\n删除卡不等于否定这些抽象动作在写作上可能有用；它只表示当前材料不足以给这些动作贴上\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01210:bc835569d733]]的标签。以后若有真正独立的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01211:0b13509d7cc2]] 材料，可以重新建立新卡，\n但不能沿用旧来源身份或旧 profile。\n\n",
